comments: Antetokounmpo (MIL) initially establishes himself in a legal screening position, but continues to move into Simmons' (PHI) path and makes contact that affects his ability to get through the pick.
Redick (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Lopez (MIL) and firms up during the screen, but he is able to move through contact.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Lopez (MIL) makes contact to Embiid's (PHI) arm during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Redick (PHI) and slightly extends his arms against his side, but he is able to move through contact.
Redick (PHI) makes marginal contact to Hill's (MIL) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Simmons (PHI) firms up during the dribble hand-off and makes marginal contact with Hill (MIL).
Redick (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Lopez (MIL) and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Lopez (MIL) maintains legal guarding position as he absorbs the contact during Embiid's (PHI) driving shot attempt.
Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Antetokounmpo (MIL) and firms up during the pick, but he is able to move through contact.
Simmons (PHI) commits a take foul on Middleton (MIL).
Redick (PHI)  makes marginal contact with Sterling (MIL) as he moves around the screen, but doesn't affect his ability to defend.
Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Hill (MIL) and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Redick (PHI) commits a take foul on Hill (MIL).
Embiid (PHI) and Lopez (MIL) engage and separate during the rebound.
